their concerns, you know, and...

01:08.135 --> 01:10.272
Hold it, hold it.

01:10.305 --> 01:11.909
Are they intentionally
underperforming

01:11.942 --> 01:13.345
in order to get their way?

01:13.378 --> 01:14.848
