of my book and I...

02:20.312 --> 02:22.016
Not the fucking book again.
Give it to me.

02:22.049 --> 02:23.218
I-I don't have it.

02:23.251 --> 02:24.955
-Yes, you do, boy.
-(sighs)

02:24.988 --> 02:26.892
