02:51.909 --> 02:54.146
And not one
that you should be asking.

02:54.180 --> 02:56.251
Let's get on with the last song.

02:56.284 --> 02:59.156
So you will be meeting
with Xerxes.

02:59.190 --> 03:02.129
Okay? He's the one
that they've elected leader.

03:02.162 --> 03:03.866
