more time for our hobbies.

03:29.383 --> 03:31.956
(clears throat)
"Number two.

03:31.989 --> 03:35.062
"We will not be blamed
for all phantom smells at work.

03:35.095 --> 03:38.235
"This is an old building
with old pipes, and the smells

03:38.268 --> 03:40.506
