kills himself.

04:35.883 --> 04:36.952
The end.

04:36.986 --> 04:38.923
(gasps)
Aha! Yes!

04:38.956 --> 04:40.960
This will do very nicely.

04:40.994 --> 04:44.166
Everyone! We're going
to the night market!

04:44.200 --> 04:47.039
A night market actually exists
in every single town.

04:47.072 --> 04:50.445
